_sText:
Re-upload of deathrun_depot version 1.3 (2015)

Requires Counter-Strike: Source textures!

Features

  • Four different endings to choose from
  • Many hidden secrets and collectibles
  • A handful of autotraps
  • Safe for 32-players
  • Auto AFK slayer
